                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Also, a click within website contract of adhesion with a box that says "yes" is not a statement under oath.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
